Justice League Case File: 061906.01

I knew Superman was in a hurry to get back to Metropolis to stop the incoming storm. But, I had the daily ritual of charging my ring to do that. - Green Lantern

Justice League Case File: 061906.10

In my short time as a superhero, I've seen and been in some powerful slugfests. None of them compare to seeing Superman take on the Parasite. - Green Lantern

Back with a new plan for global conquest, Brainiac picked a moment when I would be most vulnerable-the award ceremony at the White House. - Superman
